  "decision_conditions": [
    "The proposed two storey rear extension by reason of its excessive scale, bulk, mass and lack of subservience would appear as an unacceptably dominant and visually intrusive feature in the rear garden environment harmful to the appearance of the surrounding area contrary to Policy 26 of the Havering Local Plan, D4 of the London Plan, Emerson Park Policy Area and the Residential Extensions and Alterations Supplementary Planning Documents.",
    "The proposed two storey rear extension would, by reason of its depth, height and position close to the boundaries of the site, be an intrusive and unneighbourly development as well as having an adverse effect on the amenities of adjacent neighbours contrary to Policies 7 and 26 of the Havering Local Plan and the Residential Extensions and Alterations Supplementary Planning Document.",
